<view class="page">
  <view class="background-glow glow-top"></view>
  <view class="background-glow glow-bottom"></view>

  <view class="firefly firefly-1"></view>
  <view class="firefly firefly-2"></view>
  <view class="firefly firefly-3"></view>

  <view class="top-bar">
    <view class="back-button" bindtap="goBack">‹</view>

    <view class="top-title">
      第一个探索任务
    </view>

    <view class="top-placeholder"></view>
  </view>

  <view class="mission-label">
    任务 01
  </view>

  <view class="mission-title">
    寻找搬运大师
  </view>

  <view class="mission-card">
    <view class="character-area">
      <view class="character-glow"></view>
      <view class="ant">🐜</view>
      <view class="leaf-platform"></view>
    </view>

    <view class="character-name">
      蚂蚁
    </view>

    <view class="character-title">
      昆虫世界的搬运大师
    </view>

    <view class="dialogue">
      <view class="dialogue-line">“我好像忘记了自己的名字……”</view>
      <view class="dialogue-line">“也忘记了伙伴们去了哪里。”</view>
    </view>

    <view class="divider"></view>

    <view class="mission-description">
      请在你身边找到一只蚂蚁，
      用探索镜头帮助它恢复记忆。
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="clue-card">
    <view class="clue-header">
      <view class="clue-icon">⌖</view>
      <view class="clue-title">探索线索</view>
    </view>

    <view class="clue-list">
      <view class="clue-item">
        <view class="clue-dot"></view>
        <view class="clue-text">看看小区里的花坛边</view>
      </view>

      <view class="clue-item">
        <view class="clue-dot"></view>
        <view class="clue-text">留意树根和石缝附近</view>
      </view>

      <view class="clue-item">
        <view class="clue-dot"></view>
        <view class="clue-text">不要用手触碰或伤害它</view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="action-area">
    <button class="start-button" bindtap="beginMission">
      拿起镜头，开始寻找
    </button>

    <view class="safety-hint">
      探索时请让家长陪在身边
    </view>
  </view>
</view>